{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The very domination! Be the demon king who conquers the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;MURAYAKI VILLAIN&quot;a village-burning, female-oriented, \u2640 &gt; \u2642 Demon King Army raising dating sim</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/CHARACTER.png?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become the Demon King who is stronger than anyone else, stand on the front line, and take this world in your hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a handsome \u2640 &gt; \u2642 full-fledged villain game for those of you who want to be a dark hero of destruction rather than a protected princess.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/MV01.png?t=1738585723\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/yaki.gif?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The goal of the game is to expand the demon's territory by burning human villages and conquer the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The main character, who has lost his demon castle and all his weapons to the humans, uses ...... the &quot;frying pan&quot;!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With his assistants in tow, he sometimes clouds and draws out negative forces to put wood on the fires of hell!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/MV02.png?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/system.png?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The hero is the sole survivor of the thousands of descendants of the Demon King. Of course, the Demon King's army was destroyed by the heroes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The hero must put to work four &quot;useless&quot; demons that have survived without fighting because they were left behind, and grow the Demon King's army!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/MV03.png?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/karma.png?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Karma, which accumulates when you do bad things, is the source of the demon king's magical power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">With Karma, you can do anything you want. ......!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/MV04.png?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/comu.png?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a demon king, interacting with your subordinates is an important part of your job.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Go out for a drink or have a conversation with them to increase their loyalty!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/ENASHI.png?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is an raising dating sim for those who want to be a bad and strong woman and train a female-attacking demon king army!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So, put it on your wish list now and take the first step toward world domination!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738585723","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738585723","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738585723","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738585723","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":3240910,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The very domination! Be the demon king who conquers the world!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;MURAYAKI VILLAIN&quot;a village-burning, female-oriented, \u2640 &gt; \u2642 Demon King Army raising dating sim</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/CHARACTER.png?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become the Demon King who is stronger than anyone else, stand on the front line, and take this world in your hands!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a handsome \u2640 &gt; \u2642 full-fledged villain game for those of you who want to be a dark hero of destruction rather than a protected princess.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/MV01.png?t=1738585723\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/yaki.gif?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The goal of the game is to expan