ng?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a demon king, interacting with your subordinates is an important part of your job.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Go out for a drink or have a conversation with them to increase their loyalty!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/extras/ENASHI.png?t=1738585723\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is an raising dating sim for those who want to be a bad and strong woman and train a female-attacking demon king army!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">So, put it on your wish list now and take the first step toward world domination!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","developers":["ALENISM"],"genres":[{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2529780/header.jpg?t=1738585723","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257087854,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257087854/movie480.mp4?t=1736506646","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257087854/movie_max.mp4?t=1736506646"},"name":"Waku Waku Games News 24-DEC Edition","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257087854/7a62febd135e611f6cea6f178e07c0991d424572/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1736506646","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257087854/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1736506646","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257087854/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1736506646"}},{"highlight":true,"id":256972780,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256972780/movie480.mp4?t=1720861585","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256972780/movie_max.mp4?t=1720861585"},"name":"\u30e0\u30e9\u30e4\u30ad\u30f4\u30a3\u30e9\u3